{"tid":1986979,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民歡迎放寬食肆入座限制　不擔心風險考慮光顧堂食","createTime":"2020-04-24T07:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T07:33:27.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d58fa067cee2016710f0d060c171e48b63ccde","tid":1986979,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"政府限制食肆入座人數不可多於五成的措施，今日起放寬，在午飯時間，灣仔多間食肆大排長龍，其中一間高峰時有近20名顧客排隊等候入座。<br />\n<br />\n顧客曾先生認為，放寬限制是好事，之前因為免浪費時間排隊，多數選擇外賣，現時輪候時間縮短，會考慮增加堂食次數。<br />\n<br />\n另一位顧客陳先生也支持相關安排，認為放寬規例能幫助食肆提升生意額，近日確診數字回落，可見疫情有所緩和，因此不太擔心堂食人數增加，會增加感染風險的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522513-20200424.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522513-20200424.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=fd2ac027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522513-20200424.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=65461761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522513-20200424.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有正常腦袋的市民都歡迎放寬限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}